## DESCRIPTION
##   Approximating a Function with a Taylor Series
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## Tagged by nhamblet

## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Infinite sequences and series)
## DBsection(Taylor series)
## Institution(Rochester and Fort Lewis College)
